{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pack","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","preciseIdentifier":"c:MLNOfflineStorage.h@T@MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"pack","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The offline pack to remove.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The completion handler to call once the pack has been","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"removed. This handler is executed asynchronously on the main queue.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"As soon as this method is called on a pack, the pack becomes invalid; any","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"attempt to send it a message will result in an exception being thrown. If an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"error occurs and the pack cannot be removed, do not attempt to reuse the pack","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object. Instead, if you need continued access to the pack, suspend all packs","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and use the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks"},{"text":" method to obtain valid pointers to all the packs.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To detect when any call to this method results in a pack being removed, observe","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"KVO change notifications on the shared offline storage object’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"text":" key","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"path. Removals from that array result in an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSKeyValueChangeRemoval"},{"text":" change.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When you remove an offline pack, any resources that are required by that pack,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"but not other packs, become eligible for deletion from offline storage. Because","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the backing store used for offline storage is also used as a general purpose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"cache for map resources, such resources may not be immediately removed if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"implementation determines that they remain useful for general performance of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the map.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:"},"metadata":{"title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflineStorage(im)removePack:withCompletionHandler:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"A block to be called once an offline pack has been completely invalidated and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"removed.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackremovalcompletionhandler","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/reloadPacks":{"abstract":[{"text":"Forcibly, asynchronously reloads the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"text":" property. At some point after this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method is called, the pointer values of the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"text":" objects in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"text":" property change, even if the underlying data for these packs has not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"changed. If this method is called while a pack is actively downloading, the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"behavior is undefined.","type":"text"}],"title":"reloadPacks","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/reloadpacks","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks","type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"reloadPacks","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"title":"MLNOfflineStorage","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/removePack:withCompletionHandler:":{"abstract":[{"text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed.","type":"text"}],"title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"title":"MLNOfflinePack","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"}}}